OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and largely sunny, feeling
OL,6,Fwarm or very warm, although patchy
OL,7,Fcloud developing in places. The light
OL,8,Fbreeze strengthens during the day
OL,9,Fespecially along the south coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy overnight
OL,12,Fand dry with some occasional breaks in
OL,13,Fthe cloud. Winds easing but breezy
OL,14,Falong the coasts. Temperatures mild
OL,15,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
