OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FBreezy at times with variable
OL,6,Fcloud for much of the period, staying
OL,7,Fmostly dry with hazy sunshine at
OL,8,Ftimes. Temperatures likely above
OL,9,Faverage, becoming very warm or hot in
OL,10,Fplaces.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBreezy
OL,13,Fat times with variable cloud for much
OL,14,Fof the period, staying mostly dry with
OL,15,Fhazy sunshine at times. Temperatures
OL,16,Flikely above average, becoming very
OL,17,Fwarm or hot in places.
